175→      Requirements:
176→      - Allow AI bots (GPTBot, ChatGPT-User, Google-Extended, CCBot, ClaudeBot, anthropic-ai, Applebot, PerplexityBot, Amazonbot, FacebookBot) with explicit Allow: / rules
177→      - Include standard crawlers section (User-agent: *)
178→      - Add security/privacy Disallow rules adapted to the ${platform.name} platform
179→      - Include Sitemap directives
180→      - Add professional comments explaining each section
181→      - Format as a valid robots.txt file
182→
183→      Return ONLY the robots.txt content, no markdown fences, no extra text.
184→    `;
185→
186→    const response = await ai.models.generateContent({
187→      model: 'gemini-2.5-flash',
188→      contents: prompt,
189→      config: { temperature: 0.2 }
